    [DCS 00:22:32.480] Pipeline >   Response: To rebase your feature branch onto the latest main, first fetch the latest changes: `git fetch origin`. Then rebase: `git rebase origin/main`. If conflicts occur, resolve them, stage the resolved files with `git add`, and continue with `git rebase --continue`. To abort, use `git rebase --abort`. If your branch contains merge commits, add the `--rebase-merges` flag to preserve them.
    [DCS 00:22:32.480] Pipeline > 
    
