    [DCS 00:23:07.415] Pipeline > [ID:12] Indexes speed up reads but slow writes. Create on WHERE/JOIN/ORDER BY columns. Composite indexes use leftmost-prefix matching.
    
    [DCS 00:23:07.415] Pipeline > [ID:11] INNER JOIN: matching rows only. LEFT JOIN: all left rows. FULL OUTER JOIN: all rows from both sides. CROSS JOIN: Cartesian product.
    
